===Noun phrase===
'''[[saturation]] [[vapor pressure]]'''

#The [[vapor pressure]] at which the [[gaseous phase]] of a substance can coexist with the [[liquid phase|liquid]] or [[solid phase]] in [[equilibrium]] at a given [[temperature]].

